graph TD
    A[Start: Handle Picture Process] --> B[Initialize Camera System]
    B --> C[Capture Photo from Camera]
    C --> D{Photo Captured Successfully?}
    D -- No --> E[Log Error: Failed to Take Picture]
    E --> F[Return: Failed]
    D -- Yes --> G[Log: Picture Taken Successfully]
    G --> H{Photo Data Available?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Save Photo to File]
    I --> J{File Saved Successfully?}
    J -- No --> K[Log Warning: File Not Created]
    K --> L[Create Empty File as Backup]
    L --> M[Continue Process]
    J -- Yes --> M
    I -- Save Error --> N[Log Error: Cannot Save File]
    N --> F
    H -- No --> O[Log Error: No Photo Data Available]
    O --> F
    M --> P[Return: Success]
    P --> Q[End: Complete]
    F --> R[End: Failed]